<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer5333390832269457903">Dave Chadwick (aka SUGAR RAY DODGE) is an American graphic designer, illustrator and puppeteer. He hails from the Great State of Utah and fancies himself something of a world traveler and pompous blowhard. He has lived in Israel, Colorado, Germany, Iraq and Maryland. He is a former U.S. Army Recruiter and is a two-time Iraq War veteran.</span>

